# SonarQube MCP Integration

After generating or modifying code files, call `analyze_file_list` to check for issues.

## Workflow

1. Generate / edit code
2. Call `analyze_file_list` on changed files
3. Fix any Blocker or Critical issues before completing the task
4. Re-run analysis to confirm fixes

## Rules

- Use `search_my_sonarqube_projects` to find project keys — never guess
- Include branch parameter when working on feature branches
- After fixing issues, do NOT verify via `search_sonar_issues_in_projects` (server won't reflect updates yet)
